      "message": "[🔴 Critical] Line 67: `showOriginal` is delegate-local state and is not reset when the ListView delegate is reused for another message. A user can toggle one message, scroll, and see a different overwritten message incorrectly displaying its original body. Reset the flag when the message identity changes.\n```suggestion\nproperty bool showOriginal: false\nonIdChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\n```",
