      "message": "[🔴 Critical] Line 81: Returning `OriginalBody` directly bypasses the existing message parsing path used for `Body`, so the original view may lose sanitization/link handling/formatting consistency and may expose raw markup differently from normal messages. Parse and render the selected body through the same path instead of special-casing raw original text.\n```suggestion\nconst displayBody \u003d showOriginal \u0026\u0026 isPluginOverwrite ? OriginalBody : Body;\nif (displayBody !\u003d\u003d \"\" \u0026\u0026 ParsedBody.length \u003d\u003d\u003d 0) {\n    MessagesAdapter.parseMessage(Id, displayBody, UtilsAdapter.getAppValue(Settings.DisplayHyperlinkPreviews), rootDelegate.colorUrl, bubble.color);\n    return \"\";\n}\n```",
